Package org.jsoup.nodes

Class NodeIterator<T extends Node>

java.lang.Object
org.jsoup.nodes.NodeIterator<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterator<T>
public class NodeIterator<T extends Node> extends Object implements Iterator<T>
Iterate through a Node and its tree of descendants, in document order, and returns nodes of the specified type. This iterator supports structural changes to the tree during the traversal, such as Node.remove(), Node.replaceWith(Node), Node.wrap(String), etc.

See also the NodeTraversor if head and tail callbacks are desired for each node.

Since:
1.17.1
